	<h2>About</h2>
	<p>This plugin is my attempt to bundle the little things I wish Eleventy shipped into one optional toolkit. It leans heavily on patterns and best practices shared by the Eleventy community, and other projects like Hugo, Astro <small>or even WordPress</small>.</p>
	<p>The plugin in its current state is still an evolving piece of software so use at your own risk!</p>
